  * [armhf] dts: imx53: add support for USB armory board (Closes: #840137)
  * kconfig: Renumber SYMBOL_NEW, fixing regression of allnoconfig
    (Closes: #841357)
  * netfilter: xt_NFLOG: fix unexpected truncated packet (Closes: #841261)
  * Set ABI to 1

