    https://www.kernel.org/pub/linux/kernel/v4.x/ChangeLog-4.3.1

  [ Ben Hutchings ]
  * Set ABI to 1
  * [armhf] rtc: Enable RTC_DRV_DS1307, RTC_DRV_PCF8563, RTC_DRV_ARMADA38X
    (Closes: #807632)
