  * [x86] tls: Interpret an all-zero struct user_desc as "no segment"
    (regression in 3.16.7-ckt4)
  * net: sctp: fix slab corruption from use after free on INIT collisions
    (CVE-2015-1421)

  [ Ian Campbell ]
