  * [s390] KVM: do store status after handling STOP_ON_STOP bit
  * [s390] KVM: Sanitize fpc registers for KVM_SET_FPU
  * ACPI battery: only refresh the sysfs files when pertinent information
    changes (Closes: #670958)

